{"tid":1945746,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【手都洗爆】《怪獸與牠們的產地》女星艾歷遜失去味覺疑染上武肺","createTime":"2020-03-27T09:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:17:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d62136570155ae1e2da0957012894bfb226e3095","tid":1945746,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，電影《怪獸與牠們的產地》（Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them）35歲女星艾歷遜蘇度（Alison Sudol）亦懷疑自己中招。<br />\n<br />\n艾歷遜蘇度前日在IG上載一張在陽光下的自拍照，留言表示身體不適，但卻暫時未做武漢肺炎病毒測試：「我未有測試是因為有些人比我更需要接受測試，而且如果我沒有受到感染，去醫院檢查亦有受感染的風險。無論如何，我只是想分享經驗，這個病毒很難搞，它好像無處不在，咳嗽和發燒並不是唯一的警號。如果我們不知道自己已經受感染，我們就會散播出去，這是一個大問題。我經常都用搓手液和甚至連手都洗到爆裂，但仍然這樣，因為我們會不自覺摸自己的臉。」艾歷遜又指開始時以為只是感冒，但之後就完全失去味覺和嗅覺，連蒜頭味都聞不到，感覺自己的頭浸在魚缸一樣。艾歷遜之後去了朋友的農場自我隔離，直到看到朋友給她的文章，她才知道武漢肺炎亦有同樣的症狀。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《怪獸與牠們的產地》第三集原定於3月16日在倫敦開拍，早前已宣佈延期拍攝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200327/large/1585287105_c96b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585287105_c96b.jpg&h=1198f62d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200327/large/1585287112_bbf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585287112_bbf7.jpg&h=1e0a0fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200327/large/1585287112_e460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200327%2Flarge%2F1585287112_e460.jpg&h=fbaca44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200327/HJE35SV5GUJAEC7FII24ZVAKBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200327%2FHJE35SV5GUJAEC7FII24ZVAKBA%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNnejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=ffb6d5c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200327%2FHJE35SV5GUJAEC7FII24ZVAKBA%2F&h=9366aca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200327/HJE35SV5GUJAEC7FII24ZVAKBA/</a>"},{"pid":"86bc9741db139b6ceb2f64be3b5b945a7caf1a02","tid":1945746,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"你的樣子。。。。"}]}